title: Conceiving The Good Things of God | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Conceiving The Good Things of God | Joel Osteen
description:
God is always trying to plant seeds of hope, favor and increase into our hearts, but those seeds will never take root if we don't make an effort to believe them. If you want to see God’s promises pass over your life, you have to start by making room for them in your thinking. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
